407
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,458
SIAM SAVINGS BANK

408
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:35,541
Stay out here!

409
00:30:35,625 --> 00:30:37,541
You'll use my bank details behind my back.

410
00:30:38,833 --> 00:30:40,375
