436
00:32:10,916 --> 00:32:12,416
{\an8}Why are you bothering me?

437
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:14,833
{\an8}You understand
what "perfect fit" means, right?

438
00:32:14,916 --> 00:32:16,583
