486
00:34:37,875 --> 00:34:40,541
I think she has the right to know.

487
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:49,500
I'll go see the doctor on my own.

488
00:34:50,166 --> 00:34:52,208
I won't bother you guys.

489
00:34:52,291 --> 00:34:53,375
