598
00:42:23,250 --> 00:42:24,708
I don't remember it.

599
00:42:24,791 --> 00:42:27,250
- I'd rather climb the stairs on my own.
- Come on.

600
00:42:27,333 --> 00:42:28,750
Stretch out both of your arms.

601
00:42:29,625 --> 00:42:31,500
