702
00:49:21,458 --> 00:49:23,333
- Why?
- You can't!

703
00:49:24,666 --> 00:49:26,750
Move her back right now.

704
00:49:26,833 --> 00:49:28,083
Do it now.

705
00:49:28,166 --> 00:49:30,750
